{"title":"windows10 去除桌面快捷方式箭头","slug":"windows10-去除桌面快捷方式箭头","date":"2018-05-25T04:07:13.000Z","updated":"2018-05-29T00:04:50.451Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/windows10-去除桌面快捷方式箭头.json","photos":["https://yhloveyh.github.io/2018/05/28/%E4%B8%83%E5%BC%A0%E5%A5%BD%E7%9C%8B%E7%9A%84%E5%9B%BE/7.jpg"],"link":"","excerpt":"windows 10去除快捷方式箭头","covers":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"windows-10去除快捷方式箭头\"><a href=\"#windows-10去除快捷方式箭头\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"windows 10去除快捷方式箭头\"></a>windows 10去除快捷方式箭头</h1><a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h4 id=\"1\"><a href=\"#1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1\"></a>1</h4><p>桌面空白处新建 文本文档</p>\n<h4 id=\"2\"><a href=\"#2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2\"></a>2</h4><p>打开将如下代码粘贴到其中</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">reg add &quot;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Windows\\CurrentVersion\\Explorer\\Shell Icons&quot; /v 29 /d &quot;%systemroot%\\system32\\imageres.dll,197&quot; /t reg_sz /f</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">　　taskkill /f /im explorer.exe</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">　　attrib -s -r -h &quot;%userprofile%\\AppData\\Local\\iconcache.db&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">　   del &quot;%userprofile%\\AppData\\Local\\iconcache.db&quot; /f /q</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">　　start explorer</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">　　pause</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Ctrl + s 保存</p>\n<h4 id=\"3\"><a href=\"#3\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3\"></a>3</h4><p>修改文本文档格式 </p>\n<p>打开 <code>此电脑</code>选择 <code>查看</code>将 <code>文件拓展名</code>勾选</p>\n<p>将创建的 <code>txt</code>文档修改为 <code>bat</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"4\"><a href=\"#4\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4\"></a>4</h4><p>右键 <code>以管理员身份运行</code></p>\n<p>黑屏一下快捷方式箭头就没了</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"教程","slug":"教程","count":1,"path":"api/tags/教程.json"}]}